        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Production Deployment Best Practices"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Deploy the API behind a reverse proxy for SSL termination and load distribution. Use container orchestration tools like Kubernetes to manage scaling based on traffic patterns. Implement health checks and logging for proactive monitoring. Regularly update models via the registry without downtime by leveraging blue-green deployments. Ensure data privacy by encrypting payloads and adhering to compliance standards relevant to your domain."
